---
title: Moroccan Chicken Shawarma Bowl with Carrot Couscous & Pickled Onion
description: This earthy chicken shawarma bowl celebrates the fusion of North African and Middle-Eastern cuisine in the best way possible. Tahini lends this hearty dish deep nutty flavours while pickled red onion adds a burst of zing to balance things out. Here’s to big flavour with minimal effort!
